      "content": "but you said it's \"fundamentally a positive force.\" dont you think that's a bit biased? i mean, if ppl are saying it feels like censorship or that it's ruining free speech, isn't that just as valid a perspective as the social justice side? why is one side's view considered the \"fundamental\" one?",
