      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it feels like you're still siding with one group. you called the social justice side a \"necessary corrective,\" but you don't call the other side's concerns a \"necessary correction\" to anything—you just call them a critique. doesn't that seem like you're labeling one side as \"progress\" and the other side as just being \"against\" it, rather than actually being neutral?",
